                                <expan>beschehe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und sein hab <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist.
                            <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch, daz
                            <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
